					<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content">
<div class="mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">American political scientist (1931–2010)</div>
