<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2">
<h2 id="Death">Death</h2>
<span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Chalmers_Johnson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: Death"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span>
</div>
<p>In 2010, Chalmers Johnson died after a long illness from complications of <a href="/wiki/Rheumatoid_arthritis" title="Rheumatoid arthritis">rheumatoid arthritis</a> at his home, in <a href="/wiki/Cardiff-by-the-Sea" class="mw-redirect" title="Cardiff-by-the-Sea">Cardiff-by-the-Sea</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-14" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-14"><span class="cite-bracket">[</span>14<span class="cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup></p>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2">
